race.comment: This is tough and keep a close eye on the betting action. HIGH SECURITY (3) resumes and has switched to the Pat Webster yard. Found a place for the former trainer in a recent Toowoomba trial and he has placed fresh and at her only try over 1000m. Has the ability if presented on song. CAPIANA (2) also resumes and is good enough if forward. Has built a tidy record and will likely be positioned forward. PACIFIC PIRATE (9) resumes and is well placed at best. Has an insider barrier and the blinkers are on for the first time, signalling intent. DUCHESS OF ARGYLL (10) has been kept on the fresh side and will be around the mark with a 2kg claimer engaged.
